Package bpel.parse

Class Summary
BpelParser Parse BPEL into a tree of executable nodes
ParserElement Highest level element used for parsing text
RtstcParser Parse RTSTC input, RTSTC is a way to avoid making calls across the network by having machines running both the service they are calling and this BPEL execution engine.
XmlParser Traverse an XML tree using the DOMParser
YamlParser Very simple YAML parser, that maps YAML pairs into a hashmap
